{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Embark on a relaxing, wholesome, flavorful trip and cook up an unforgettable journey through the very birthplace of the Universe</strong></i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Engulf yourself in a colorful after world</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Taste of Heaven</strong></i> encapsulates a delicate blend between a cooking game and an RPG, in which creativity and strategy are interwoven within a world of flavors. Along your celestial journey, you will get to craft unique dishes for gods, but you will also have to satiate every hungry soul out there. Who knows? You might even be able to charm some of the divine spirits wandering in this scrumptious and vibrant land of eternal dreams.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835080/extras/LeGIF.gif?t=1731282680\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Cook within the divine</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover our unique and seamless recipe system that invites you to use every ingredient and tools at your disposal to satisfy waves of hungry, demanding customers. Be careful, though, as each of them has their own distinctive personality and unique challenges!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835080/extras/SteamPage_BookRecipes.png?t=1731282680\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Mingle with gods and godlings</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <i><strong>Taste of Heaven</strong></i>, you'll encounter an eccentric cast of characters, intriguing creatures, and souls with some\u2026 unresolved issues. Be prepared to wine and dine some lonely souls in order to deepen bonds, because there might also be a pinch of romance on the menu.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835080/extras/Vignette_Character_B.png?t=1731282680\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Shape each run into a unique journey</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover a plethora of items, perks, hidden secrets and unique events, which will turn each run into a one-of-a-kind adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835080/extras/Steam_PerksChoice.png?t=1731282680\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Make a home in the void</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gather resources and build your own hotel within the belly of a giant fish. Along the way, travelers will stop by, each bringing a helping hand and a story to share as you blossom your own peaceful oasis for them to unwind and relax.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835080/extras/ryokan.png?t=1731282680\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835080/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731282680","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835080/page.bg.jpg?t=1731282680","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835080/b6e4efa5896bd0e807475b3ac0950cca54271d67/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1731282680","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835080/b6e4efa5896bd0e807475b3ac0950cca54271d67/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1731282680","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Embark on a relaxing, wholesome, flavorful trip and cook up an unforgettable journey through the very birthplace of the Universe</strong></i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Engulf yourself in a colorful after world</strong></h2><